  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A clicker with an ending? What do you mean? <br> <br><strong><i>Just a Village Clicker</i></strong>  is a clicker game (wow), where you collect resources to rebuild your village and help the villagers with their tasks. <br> <br>Improve your village and combat stats with over <strong>50 available upgrades</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras/8025c2f4c7f17b4c5e2cf125c38effe3.avif?t=1735039209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras_big/8025c2f4c7f17b4c5e2cf125c38effe3.avif?t=1735039209 width=800 height=120 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know the villagers better, their specialties, and their stories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras/4d89010b3549c94e5ffa29f485ecaf74.avif?t=1735039209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras_big/4d89010b3549c94e5ffa29f485ecaf74.avif?t=1735039209 width=800 height=379 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through the dungeon floors and defeat powerful enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras/726192dc627b4d17b6d0d4f9b03a6663.avif?t=1735039209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras_big/726192dc627b4d17b6d0d4f9b03a6663.avif?t=1735039209 width=800 height=253 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br>All of this just one click away! (Well, actually several clicks!)</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A clicker with an ending? What do you mean? <br> <br><strong><i>Just a Village Clicker</i></strong>  is a clicker game (wow), where you collect resources to rebuild your village and help the villagers with their tasks. <br> <br>Improve your village and combat stats with over <strong>50 available upgrades</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras/8025c2f4c7f17b4c5e2cf125c38effe3.avif?t=1735039209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras_big/8025c2f4c7f17b4c5e2cf125c38effe3.avif?t=1735039209 width=800 height=120 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know the villagers better, their specialties, and their stories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras/4d89010b3549c94e5ffa29f485ecaf74.avif?t=1735039209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras_big/4d89010b3549c94e5ffa29f485ecaf74.avif?t=1735039209 width=800 height=379 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through the dungeon floors and defeat powerful enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras/726192dc627b4d17b6d0d4f9b03a6663.avif?t=1735039209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316510/extras_big/726192dc627b4d17b6d0d4f9b03a6663.avif?t=1735039209 width=800 height=253 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br>All of this just one click away! (Well, actually several clicks!)</p>",
